data.legacy-decorators#Legacy Decorators:
Next.js will automatically detect experimentalDecorators in jsconfig.json or tsconfig.json. Legacy decorators are commonly used with older versions of libraries like mobx.This flag is only supported for compatibility with existing applications. We do not recommend using legacy decorators in new applications.First, update to the latest version of Next.js: npm install next@latest. Then, update your jsconfig.json or tsconfig.json file:
{
  "compilerOptions": {
    "experimentalDecorators": true
  }
}

